Path-Find version 0.01
======================

Finding files in a directory and its subdirectories.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Test::More
    Text::Glob
    File::Spec
    Scalar::Util

